 die Rubrik einer interkulturellen Literaturgeschichte.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aIndirekte Kommunikation. 4aKonversationsliteratur. 4aKunst des Impliziten. 4aexception culturelle. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / French.2bisacsh  aArt of the implicit.  aConversational literature.  aCultural exception.  aIndirect communication.0 cEPUBz97831107581080 cprintz978311075765140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110758009zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110758009zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110758009/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA